text: Mohammed Ouseb (born July 17, 1974 in Tsumeb) is a Namibian footballer. He previously played for South Africa's Premier Soccer League clubs Kaizer Chiefs, Moroka Swallows and Norway's FC Lyn Oslo as well as Chief Santos in his home country.
